<text><body>
<lb n="0490b20"/>
<milestone unit="juan" n="1"/>
<lb n="0490b21"/><head type="no">No. 1325</head><div1 type="jing">
<lb n="0490b22"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><note n="0490027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】麗本</note>佛說療痔病經</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0490b23"/>
<lb n="0490b24"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0490028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔大〕－【三】</note><note n="0490028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔大〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0490028"><lem>大</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>唐三<note n="0490029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">藏＋（法師）【三】</note><note n="0490029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">藏＋（法師）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0490029"><lem>藏</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">藏法師</rdg></app>義淨<note n="0490030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔奉制〕－【三】</note><note n="0490030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔奉制〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0490030"><lem>奉　制</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>譯</byline>
<lb n="0490b25"/><p>如是我聞。一時薄伽梵。在王舍大城竹林園
<lb n="0490b26"/>中。與大苾芻眾五百人俱。時有眾多苾芻身
<lb n="0490b27"/>患痔病。形體羸瘦痛苦縈纏。於日夜中極受
<lb n="0490b28"/>憂惱。時具壽阿難陀見是事已詣世尊所。頂
<lb n="0490b29"/>禮雙足在一面立。<note n="0490031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">白＋（佛）【三】</note><note n="0490031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">白＋（佛）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0490031"><lem>白</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">白佛</rdg></app>言世尊。今王舍城多有
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1325.0490c" n="0490c"/>
<lb n="0490c01"/>苾芻。身患痔病形體羸瘦痛苦縈纏。於日夜
<lb n="0490c02"/>中極受憂惱。世尊此諸<note n="0490032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">痔病＝病苦【三】</note><note n="0490032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">痔病＝病苦【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0490032"><lem>痔病</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">病苦</rdg></app>云何救療。<note n="0490033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（爾時）＋佛【三】</note><note n="0490033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（爾時）＋佛【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0490033"><lem>佛</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">爾時佛</rdg></app>
<lb n="0490c03"/>告阿難陀汝可聽此療痔病經。讀誦受持繫
<lb n="0490c04"/>心勿忘。亦於他人廣為宣說。此諸痔病悉得
<lb n="0490c05"/>除<note n="0490034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">差＝殄【三】</note><note n="0490034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">差＝殄【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0490034"><lem>差</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">殄</rdg></app>。所謂風痔熱痔&CB00486;痔三合痔。血痔腹中
<lb n="0490c06"/>痔鼻內痔。齒痔舌痔眼痔耳痔。頂痔手足痔
<lb n="0490c07"/>脊背痔<note n="0490035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">屎＝糞門【三】</note><note n="0490035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">屎＝糞門【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0490035"><lem>屎</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">糞門</rdg></app>痔。遍身支節所生諸痔。如是痔&CB00485;
<lb n="0490c08"/>悉皆乾燥。墮落消滅<note n="0490036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">畢差＝必瘥【三】</note><note n="0490036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">畢差＝必瘥【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0490036"><lem>畢差</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">必瘥</rdg></app>無疑。皆應誦持如
<lb n="0490c09"/>是神&CB00057;。即說&CB00057;曰</p>
<lb n="0490c10"/><note n="0490037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔怛姪…云〕二十五字－【三】</note><note n="0490037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔怛姪…云〕二十五字－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0490037" word-count="25"><lem><p type="dharani">怛姪他　揭賴米　室利　室利　魔揭室
<lb n="0490c11"/>至三磨&CB04133;都莎訶</p>
<lb n="0490c12"/><p>此&CB00057;<note place="inline">丹藏云</note></p></lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0490c13"/><p type="dharani">怛姪他　頞闌帝　頞藍謎　室利鞞　室里
<lb n="0490c14"/>室里　磨羯失質　三婆跋&CB00418;　莎訶</p>
<lb n="0490c15"/><p>阿難陀於此北方有大雪山王。中有大<note n="0490038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">莎＝娑【三】</note><note n="0490038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">莎＝娑【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0490038"><lem>莎</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">娑</rdg></app>羅
<lb n="0490c16"/>樹名曰難勝。有三種華。一者初生二者圓滿。
<lb n="0490c17"/>三者乾枯。猶如彼華乾燥落時。我<note n="0490039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">諸＋（苾芻所患）【三】</note><note n="0490039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">諸＋（苾芻所患）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0490039"><lem>諸</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">諸苾芻所患</rdg></app>痔病亦
<lb n="0490c18"/>復如是。勿復血出亦勿膿流。永除苦痛悉<note n="0490040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">皆＋（平復即令）【三】</note><note n="0490040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">皆＋（平復即令）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0490040"><lem>皆</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">皆平復即令</rdg></app>
<lb n="0490c19"/>乾燥。又復若常誦此經者。得<note n="0490041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">宿＋（命）【三】</note><note n="0490041" resp="CBETA" type="mod">宿＋（命）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0490041"><lem>宿</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">宿命</rdg></app>住智能憶過
<lb n="0490c20"/>去七生之事。&CB00057;法成就莎訶。又說&CB00057;曰</p>
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1325.0491a" n="0491a"/>
<lb n="0491a01"/><p type="dharani">怛姪他<note n="0491001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">占米＝苫謎【宋】【明】＊，苦謎【元】＊</note><note n="0491001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">占米＝苫謎【宋】【明】＊，＝苦謎【元】＊</note><app n="0491001"><lem>占米</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】" resp="Taisho">苫謎</rdg><rdg wit="【元】" resp="Taisho">苦謎</rdg></app>　<app type="＊" source="0491001"><lem>占米</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】">苫謎</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">苦謎</rdg></app>捨<note n="0491002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">占米＝苫謎【三】</note><note n="0491002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">占米＝苫謎【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0491002"><lem>占米</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">苫謎</rdg></app>　<note n="0491003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">占＝苫【宋】【明】，苦【元】</note><note n="0491003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">占＝苫【宋】【明】，＝苦【元】</note><app n="0491003"><lem>占</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】" resp="Taisho">苫</rdg><rdg wit="【元】" resp="Taisho">苦</rdg></app><note n="0491004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">沒&CB00135;＝末泥去【宋】【明】，末泥【元】</note><note n="0491004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">沒&CB00135;＝末泥去【宋】【明】，＝末泥【元】</note><app n="0491004"><lem>沒&CB00135;</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】" resp="Taisho">末泥去</rdg><rdg wit="【元】" resp="Taisho">末泥</rdg></app>捨
<lb n="0491a02"/><note n="0491005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">占＝苫【三】</note><note n="0491005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">占＝苫【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0491005"><lem>占</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">苫</rdg></app>泥　莎訶</p>
<lb n="0491a03"/><p>佛說是經已。時具壽阿難陀及諸大眾。皆大
<lb n="0491a04"/>歡喜信受奉行</p>
<lb n="0491a05"/><juan fun="close" n="001"><jhead>佛說療痔病經</jhead></juan></div1>
